title: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
description: Over a year after the events of Venom (2018), investigative journalist Eddie Brock struggles to adjust to life as the host of the alien symbiote Venom, which grants him super-human abilities in order to be a lethal vigilante. Brock attempts to reignite his career by interviewing serial killer Cletus Kasady, who becomes the host of the symbiote Carnage and escapes prison after a failed execution.

imdbInfo.ratingReason: Rated PG-13 for intense sequences of violence and action, some strong language, disturbing material and suggestive references
